## MPD controls
alt + {Page_Down,Page_Up,p}
	mpc {next,prev,toggle}
alt + {k,j}
	mpc volume {+5,-5}
alt + {comma,period}
	mpc seek {-2%,+2%}

## dmenu
super + e
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/dmenuunicode
super + d
	dmenu_run

## Play YouTube in MPV
super + y
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/youtube-mpv

## Print Screen Commands
Print
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/scrot/fullscreen
ctrl + Print
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/scrot/selection
shift + Print
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/scrot/window
ctrl + shift + Print
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/scrot/select_window

## Open Applications
super + f
	dolphin
super + Return
	rxvt-unicode
super + b
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/delete-history
ctrl + Escape
	rxvt-unicode -geometry 160x100 -e htop
super + l
	/home/thasharath/.scripts/open-link
